---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="">
					<div class="col-12 col-sm-10 offset-sm-1 col-lg-7 offset-lg-0 col-xl-7 offset-xl-1 col-xxl-6 offset-xxl-2 mb-4">
						<h1>Welcome.</h1>
						<p>
							My name is Sascha Loishandl, and I'm a software developer based in Austria.
							While I specialize in web development, I also have extensive experience in many other areas such as desktop application development,
							database and software architecture, game development, and Linux server management.	
						</p>
						<p>
							I invite you to explore my game development projects on <a href="https://saschalois.itch.io/" target="_blank">itch.io</a>
							and <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/search/?developer=Lois" target="_blank">Steam</a>.	
						</p>
						<p>
							I'm an advocate for open-source software.
							You can find my contributions and projects on my <a href="https://github.com/loissascha" target="_blank">GitHub</a> profile.	
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="col-12 col-sm-10 offset-sm-1 col-lg-4 offset-lg-1 col-xl-3 offset-xl-1">
						<h2>Projects</h2>
						<ul>
							<li>
								<h5>
									<a href="/projects/mysqlmanager">MySql Manager</a> 
									<small>
										<span class="badge bg-blazor">Blazor</span>
										<span class="badge bg-csharp">C#</span>
									</small> 
								</h5>
								<small>A comprehensive tool for managing MySQL databases locally or remotely over the internet.</small>	
							</li>
							<li>
								<h5>
									<a href="https://github.com/loissascha/linbench" target="_blank">CPU Benchmarking Tool</a>
									<small>
										<span class="badge bg-blazor">Blazor</span>
										<span class="badge bg-csharp">C#</span>
									</small>
								</h5>
								<small>A versatile CPU benchmarking tool, optimized for Linux but compatible with all systems.</small>
							</li>
							<li>
								<h5>
									<a href="https://github.com/loissascha/randomWallpaperPicker" target="_blank">Random Wallpaper Changer</a>
									<small><span class="badge bg-rust">Rust</span></small>
								</h5>
								<small>CLI tool written in Rust that changes your wallpaper to a random image from a provided path.</small>
							</li>
							<li>
								<h5>
									<a href="https://saschalois.itch.io/hells-last-stand" target="_blank">Hells Last Stand</a>
									<small>
										<span class="badge bg-godot">Godot</span>
										<span class="badge bg-csharp">C#</span>
									</small>
								</h5>
								<small>An intense game developed during the GDTV 2024 Game Jam.</small>
							</li>
							<li>
								<h5>
									<a href="/projects/test">Test</a>
								</h5>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
</Layout>
<style>
	h1 {
		font-size: 4rem;
	}
	
	h2 {
		background: #f38ba8;
		color: #1e1e2e;
		padding: 10px;
		border-top-left-radius: 15px;
		border-bottom-left-radius: 15px;
	}
	
	ul {
		list-style: none;
	}
	
	li {
		margin-top: 15px;
	}
	
	a {
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: bold; 
	}
	
	
	.bg-blazor {
		background: #cba6f7;
		color: #1e1e2e;
	}
	
	.bg-csharp {
		background: #a6e3a1;
		color: #1e1e2e;
	}
	
	.bg-rust {
		background: #f38ba8;
		color: #1e1e2e;
	}
	
	.bg-godot {
		background: #89b4fa;
		color: #1e1e2e;
	}
</style>